<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[85717]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[Dialogues between music and cinema come to Sant Pau]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[The pianist Jordi Sabatés' compositions will be holding a dialogue with the magic of the silent cinema of Buster Keaton and Segundo de Chomón.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>The Sant Pau Modernista Site offers a re-discovery of Buster Keaton&#8217;s <strong>Sherlock Junior</strong><i></i> and a selection of films from Segundo de Chomón, with a live music accompaniment courtesy of pianist and composer, Jordi Sabatés.</p>
<p>This activity is the first in the Autumn-Winter Sant Pau Premiere Cycle. The exciting action scenes in the Buster Keaton film will be set to piano music by Jordi Sabatés who will also be giving a live performance of the music he has composed for fifteen films from Segundo de Chomón, one of the greatest exponents of primitive visual experimental cinema of the 20th century.</p>
